title: EP.50: LEBRON IN SEATTLE, KAMARU USMAN, BIG BETS, UPCOMING GIVEAWAY, FANTASY FOOTBALL AND MUCH MORE!
description: Lebron James finally made his way out to Seattle and the crowd proves the people of Seattle need the Super Sonics back. Kamaru Usman loses his championship belt. Griffin and Joe get creative with their upcoming bets and announce the coming jersey giveaway for epidsode 52. Tune in for some fantasy football and much more!
